-- Queens Park Rangers Striker Helguson Signs New Contract to 2013
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2011-12-29T10:26:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-29/queens-park-rangers-striker-helguson-signs-new-contract-to-2013.html
Queens Park Rangers striker Heidar
Helguson signed a new contract through the summer of 2013, the
club said on its website.  Helguson, 34, has seven goals in 12 Premier League matches
this season. The Iceland international has scored 26 times since
joining QPR from Bolton during the 2008-09 season.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  